train/pick_and_place_simple-CD-None-Dres:
(:goal
	(exists (?r - receptacle)
(exists (?o - object)
(exists (?lo - location)
(exists (?ll - agent)
(and 
		(objectType ?o CDType)
		(atLocation ?ll ?lo)
		(receptacleType ?r DresserType)
		(not (inReceptacle ?o ?r)))))))
)
train/look_at_obj_in_light-Pen-None-Floo:
(:goal
	(exists (?ot - object)
(exists (?o - object)
(exists (?l - location)
(exists (?a - agent)
(and 
		(objectType ?ot FloorLampType)
		(toggleable ?ot)
		(isToggled ?ot)
		(objectAtLocation ?ot ?l)
		(atLocation ?a ?l)
		(objectType ?o PenType)
		(holds ?a ?o))))))
)
